name: ꧁•⊹٭𝚗𝚒𝚐𝚑𝚝 𝚙𝚊𝚕𝚞𝚍𝚊𝚛𝚒𝚞𝚖٭⊹•꧂
description: The Latin word “Palus” means marsh or swamp, and “arium” means a place. This is a semi-aquatic habitat that can house a broad range of terrestrial, aquatic and semi-aquatic plants and animals. In this specific paludarium you can find fluorescent minerals, shimmery white animals, alien rocks and branches from ancient trees. All this biome covered by an eternal night veil. Take good care of this paludarium and watch it bloom!
